    {
      "responseId": "66666666-6666-4666-8666-666666666666",
      "message": "Place them near a south-facing window where they get the most light, and rotate the pots weekly so they grow evenly. If daylight is short, a small grow light for a few hours helps. Keep them away from cold drafts and blasting radiators.",
